  "original_title": "2,973 \u0b90\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b95\u0ba8\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A suspect was arrested by customs officials with 2,973 ice pills",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Customs media spokesperson, a suspect was arrested by the Customs officials with a drug called methamphetamine or ice valued at two crore ninety seven hundred thirty thousand rupees at the Central Post Office in Colombo today. .",
        "In this case the said package was sent by air mail from Netherlands to Colombo Central Post Office to the address given to a foot masseur in Gampaha Ganemulla.",
        "In this case, on the basis of suspicion, when the customs officials inspected the machine in the said package, 2,973 methamphetamine pills weighing 01 kg 189 grams were found.",
        "In this case, the person at the address mentioned in the package had also come to the Central Post Exchange in Colombo to receive the said package, but he was arrested by the customs officials.",
        "Officials of the Postal Department of the Colombo Central Post Exchange and officers of the Police Anti-Narcotics Unit also assisted in the arrest.",
        "It is noteworthy that the stock of drugs and the person who came to carry them have been handed over to the Police Narcotics Unit for further investigation."
      ],
